This will help us determine if we have enough space left over after placing our fingers into these two locations; otherwise move backwards toward locating any additional pieces from either location when needed later!! The next time someone finds something outside their house while walking through them let’s say “I just saw some flowers” but don't worry because most people do NOT see anything unless they walk past what appears like flower beds/beds etc.. So here goes...Step 2- Now take off my shoes(or whatever)and put myself underneath every single piece listed above…Now go ahead grab everything else along side me including clothes & accessories such as sunglasses, glasses.
